FAQ

Which frameworks do you support?

We support all major RedM frameworks and can work with any custom setup:

VORPRSGQBCoreRedEM RPCustom Frameworks
How long does the setup take?

Standard setups typically take 2-4 hours. Premium setups with custom configurations may take 4-8 hours depending on complexity. We aim to complete most setups within 24 hours.

What payment methods do you accept?

We accept PayPal. Payment details will be provided when you contact us via Discord.

Do you offer support after setup?

Yes! All packages include basic post-setup support via Discord. Premium packages include extended assistance to help you get started smoothly.

Can I request custom configurations?

Absolutely! The Premium package includes custom request implementation. For Standard packages, custom work can be added for an additional fee.
